main event: An unidentified flying object was sighted in Camden, New Jersey on August 25, 1957 by Des Ballasco.
interesting points: The report was part of Project Blue Book,The sighting was documented under file number 300 24-190,The document mentions the inclusion of a photograph that is not present,A black-and-white image of a rectangle with a dark background was noted,The sighting involved an unidentified flying object.
